{"tid":242704,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"除咗要做security update, 大家有用router嘅, 最好......","createTime":"2017-05-14T06:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T16:25:40.000Z","uid":33883,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"84fcfe464cb674574c62d1fb2965cb8798e94998","tid":242704,"uid":33883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"A. 下面堆ports<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好放出街</span>:<br />\n22 SSH<br />\n23 Telnet<br />\n135 DCE<br />\n137-139 NBT<br />\n145 UAAC<br />\n445 SMB<br />\n3389 RDP<br />\n<br />\nB. DMZ要<span style=\"color: red;\">disabled</span><br />\n<br />\nC. UPnP要<span style=\"color: red;\">disabled</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有:<br />\nIntranet/home network嘅SMB全部最好disabled, 要做file transfer就改用FTP!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以放心少少咁上網, 免受WannaCrypt攻擊喇! <br />\n<br />\nAnyway, common sense最緊要! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7deeb38b4396fdb69b0f802068d19b7c9bca874","tid":242704,"uid":60249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"636ae25f23107ee4c65eb98ecebefb335684bd5d","tid":242704,"uid":111019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"熄左upnp會唔會令network內device detect唔到Wi-Fi printer同smart tv之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c0bb5c5651abcbcfba4d68d18bf9bed1178a6a","tid":242704,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"UPnP..."},{"pid":"bbe77e1bc5593f19c3f723afcf13fdb2c52eeb22","tid":242704,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:26:34.000Z","msg":"Apple tv<br />\nAirplay呢d係用咩 <br />\noff左會唔會影響"},{"pid":"29ab838cbc3528e2e5f29e90253bd80c843e0340","tid":242704,"uid":44211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:30:43.000Z","msg":"Intranet/home network嘅SMB全部最好disabled, 要做file transfer就改用FTP!<br />\n下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82101e626835ca1a3c413a436302cba174f0acb1","tid":242704,"uid":88588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:32:43.000Z","msg":"改用FTP ? 都話 common sense好緊要架啦"},{"pid":"f2b782b893a3feb88114e1cdcf280702b8f690a7","tid":242704,"uid":44211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改用FTP ? 都話 common sense好緊要架啦</blockquote><br />\nftp傳送無加密, 有機會比人cap到data <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家都係smbv1有事, 好似ssl3.0咁有根本性問題咁<br />\n唔通連tls 1.1, 1.2, 1.3都唔用, https 443 port都要封咩, 玩咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24410ae72555f12ef4f629a9eb1b55df32617cfa","tid":242704,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:57:18.000Z","msg":"呢隻毒就係透過SMB火燒連環船, 如果有一部機瀨咗嘢, 就會一嘢波及network neighborhood上所有無辜, 用FTP就起碼唔會一嘢傳染晒!<br />\n<br />\n但個個人情況都唔同,  我又冇話你地一定要跟足, 有人為求方便要冒險我都阻唔到你, 你地可以唔跟架喎, 用common sense自己執生囉! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f9c6b4d42919b37160905971601791ed0aaa23","tid":242704,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>改用FTP ? 都話 common sense好緊要架啦</blockquote><br />\nftp傳送無加密, 有機會比人cap到data <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家都係smbv1有事, 好似ssl3.0咁有根本性問題咁<br />\n唔通連tls 1.1, 1.2, 1.3都唔用, https 443 port都要封咩, 玩咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇番我個講解啦, OK? BTW, 我又唔係你肚裏面條蟲, 識嘢嘅就自己執生啦! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b74ddf3fb5868c9f217ea95334b3d640a1251b","tid":242704,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T21:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A. 下面堆ports<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好放出街</span>:<br />\n22 SSH<br />\n23 Telnet<br />\n135 DCE<br />\n137-139 NBT<br />\n145 UAAC<br />\n445 SMB<br />\n3389 RDP<br />\n<br />\nB. DMZ要<span style=\"color: red;\">disabled</span><br />\n<br />\nC. UPnP要<span style=\"color: red;\">disabled</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有:<br />\nIntranet/home network嘅SMB全部最好disabled, 要做file transfer就改用FTP!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以放心少少咁上網, 免受WannaCrypt攻擊喇! <br />\n<br />\nAnyway, common sense最緊要! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWhy do you want any port to be exported, let alone a list or ports？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：I once forwarded ssh port of a linux server at home to my router so that I can access it from work but I used password less login with public/private key."},{"pid":"c4f96088901d5f66b415c05329f569c74a7b9892","tid":242704,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T00:49:10.000Z","msg":"搭單問下，中國牌子的router可唔可靠？"},{"pid":"aa7a9d545a151b4603ca9118d5e7a1b41fef289b","tid":242704,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:12:37.000Z","msg":"呢度D人一係就覺得自己好醒最鍾意challenge人, 但永遠自己唔會出suggest<br />\n一係就太蠢, 完全唔知你講緊咩同係咁問問題, 永遠唔識自己google<br />\n洗鬼出post提佢地咩"},{"pid":"1012c0713cb8b60c7d3bbfe6f6d9e28de527580e","tid":242704,"uid":49501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"你的資訊很有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a0df0a8d2f8209d70ee6d3708c0372c79a99bd","tid":242704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:45:33.000Z","msg":"點樣 set ?"},{"pid":"185e9b0182bb14a733a527dd31069368bb3b5fce","tid":242704,"uid":64078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"973